<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>FAQ</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="login-body">
      <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

      <div class="faq-form faq-static">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>What payment methods do you accept?</h3>
          <p>This is a demo site with a mocked checkout. No actual payment is needed.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Do you offer real shipping?</h3>
          <p>No, this project is for educational purposes. All features are simulated.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Can I return products?</h3>
          <p>There is no real fulfillment. You can remove items from your cart at any time.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Is my data safe?</h3>
          <p>Passwords are hashed using bcrypt. This project follows basic security best practices.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Who built this site?</h3>
          <p>This site was developed by students as part of a college project.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>Ask Us Anything</h2>
      <form id="faqForm" class="faq-form" action="/faq" method="POST">
        <label for="question">Your Question:</label>
        <textarea name="question" id="question" placeholder="Type your question here..." required></textarea>
        <button class="btn" type="submit">Submit</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
